column5: I was just curious to know how many high school students were members on this board as I am, and would like to wish all good luck with the upcoming exams..
I haven't been for a very long time, but still rembember year end exams...good luck all....  Maureen
yep i am, grade 12. cant wait for exams to be over so i can get out fishin lol
The best 6 years of my life were in high school.
most people don't know just how great high school was till they have been working for 10 years or so..,.......and the summers off..wasn't that great
I am. Exams? DANG! next week eh, oh well. I headin up to blue mountain for a weekend of mountain biking with my buddies. Let the cramming commence!
i know eh dude..less than a week b4 the first exam and i haven't even opened a book yet

you must of been one of those smart kids lol  I did the same program but really all the time i spent at school i should never have got out of grade 9.  good thing i did good on the exams and they didnt care about attendance like they do now.  Good luck to all in there exams!  Cheers!
High school,where I  experimented everything,well almost everything.Life was great back then.  Terry whats a talk,n about,you get the summers off still.LOL
High school ya I went in the late 70's early eighties.Good luck with all the exams.MTP
